ActOther Than Statutory Authority
PrecisAppointment of WAYNE JENKINSON of Ottawa, Ontario, a duly qualified engineer and Executive Director of the National Hydrologic Service, Monitoring Data Services Directorate at Environment and Climate Change, to be the Canadian accredited officer to carry out the provisions of the Treaty with respect to the St. Mary and Milk Rivers, to hold office during pleasure.
